name: e.lements of Star Wars Ep. I, II, III
description:
************Limited Time************
***Star Wars Weekends Sale Price***

In a companion to our original e.lements of Star Wars characters from the original trilogy episodes: IV, V, and VI, we present a new design based on Star Wars episodes I, II, and III. 

Just as we did with the first print in the series, this list of e.lements is derived from the main characters per the cast credits of the movie. 

We have broken the categories into: Jedi, Droid, Comrades (friends and family of the Skywalker clan), Royal Court, Sith, Trade Federation, Rogues (not necessarily all bad, but sketchy to say the least) and the Politico.

As part of the print, there is also a key that showcase the main features of each element: element ID, element name, cast order in the film, episode, and actor(s) initials.

There are lots more characters, both credited and uncredited in these three film but we settled on all of the major characters as well as an acceptable number of secondary characters through all three films.

Printed on 13"X19 Epson 51lb/192 g/m² Ultra Premium Matte Paper with Canon's ChromaLife100 system2. This combines the benefits of genuine Canon dye-based ink and photo paper with FINE print head technology to produce long-lasting, beautiful prints with a wide color gamut for vivid coloration.

We are currently only shipping within the United States but are actively looking into providing shipping to Canada and other international destinations.

name: The Elements of Attractions
description:
This is first in a new series of a fine-art posters that present the Magic Kingdom® in a Periodic Table of Elements of Attractions for the Disney-theme parks around the world. Based on the rides and restaurants in the Magic Kingdom Park®, at the Walt Disney World® Resort in Florida, these posters reduce the attractions to simple elemental graphics comprised of element: ID, Name, latitude, longitude, park ID#, etc. This integrated design is also utilized across mediums, in clothing, prints and apps in iOS App Store and iBooks Store Printed on 13"X19 Epson 51lb/192 g/m² Ultra Premium Matte Paper with Canon's ChromaLife100 system2. This combines the benefits of genuine Canon dye-based ink and photo paper with FINE print head technology to produce long-lasting, beautiful prints with a wide color gamut for vivid coloration. We are currently only shipping within the United States but are actively looking into providing shipping to Canada and other international destinations.

Details

All of our items tend to ship within 3-5 days of order. All 13"x19" giclee prints are rolled and shipped via priority mail within the U.S.A. If you would like something mailed EXPRESS, please let us know and we will let you know how much it will cost. Alternatively, custom requests can be made by direct inquiry and we will provide a direct response.

About Us and Our Work

Having worked for some of the greatest companies in the destination tourism, entertainment and personal expression markets, designoMatt has been creating illustrations, designs, photographs and more for over 20 years now. Our store offers some of our most favorite designs and imagery for sale. We will also produce works by commission if you wish to contact us directly. Our giclée (a new word created in 1991, but used commonly today to reference high-end ink-jet prints on fine papers) prints are produced using Canon's ChromaLife100 system dye-based inks and various fine art papers (i.e. matte, glossy, peark, etc.). Using the finest quality tools to produce our work insures resistance to real-world conditions that can cause an image to fade.

Additional Information

We are available for custom orders as well as private commissions from personal and corporate buyers. Please contact us directly with your requests. designoMatt retains copyright. No reproduction of our imagery is allowed without permission from artist. All rights reserved. Finally, if you have any questions please contact us. We want you to be happy with your purchase and wish to provide all answers before you purchase your item(s).
